programme.title: Bidadari: Merah Gaun Pengantin Ep10
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Almy bertemu pemuda kaya yang sombong bernama Heykal yang belajar di kolej yang sama dengannya. Almy berkawan baik dengan Faisal dan Nadia hingga terperangkap dengan cinta tiga segi. Masa sama Almy menjalin hubungan baik dengan Datin Balqis yang mengagumi bakatnya dalam bidang perunding perkahwinan. Datin Balqis menawarkan Almy menjadi perunding perkahwinan untuk anaknya, Heykal dengan Suzie. Pada mulanya Almy menolak tetapi akhinya dia berubah fikiran. Heykal menyesal dengan sikap sombongnya terhadap Almy dan akhirnya jatuh cinta. Masa yang sama Almy pula jatuh cinta dengan Faisal. Siapakah jejaka yang menjadi pilihan Almy? Pelakon: Syafiq Kyle, Nad Zainal, Fazreen Rafi, Falisha Crossley, Syed Ali, Faye Kusairi, Mimi Ernida, Alif Hadi, Nor Albaniah, Norlia Ghani, Rahim Omar, Mubarak Majid, dan Raja Ema.

programme.title: Cuit-Cuit: Kisah 1 Rumah Ep1
programme.desc: Drama kehidupan yang mengisahkan Ika yang bekerja di sebuah caf serta Shira merupakan penyewa bilik di sebuah rumah kedai. Pada satu hari, pasangan bernama Suhaidi dan isterinya Wulan telah datang ke rumah tersebut untuk menyewa rumah mereka. Ika mengambil keputusan untuk terus tinggal di bilik sewanya dan mencari kerja di tempaty kerja Elyn, rakan serumahnya setelah tamat kolej. Namun tindakannya yang tidak memberitahu tuan rumah, telah mengundang padah! Pelakon: Nur Risteena Munir, Natasya Elyza, Abon, Raja Ema, Najwa Nasir, Kishvin, Jasmin Hamid, Hadi Tahir, Aninth Aqila, Aliff Hadi, Nur Natasya Mahyan, Zaidi Omar, Aziz M. Osman, dan Cico.

programme.title: Spektra: Saat Aku Berpaling Ep5
programme.desc: 13 tahun berlalu, tiba-tiba Hisham kembali bersama anaknya, Faizal ke rumah Saudi. Namun, pertanyaan bertubi-tubi daripada Saudi tentang Rosnah, Farid dan Faizah mengundang kemarahan dan mengganggu emosi Hisham. Apa sebenarnya berlaku? Faizal berhasil menemui keluarga yang lama terpisah, namun kehadirannya tidak diterima baik oleh Farid dan Faizah. Rosnah hanya mampu melihat Hashim dari jauh, masih berat untuk mendekati bekas suaminya itu. Pelakon: Nafiez Zaidi, Haeriyanto Hassan, Jay Iswazir, Suriati Baharom, Ziema Din, Ferth Jasni, Khairil Anwar Aman, Dayang Areeda, Abil Kamaruzaman, Mysara Sufya, Asri Ismail, Kamarool Hj Yusof, Saidi Sabri, Norhamiza Nor, Dhiya Zana, Rashdan Baba, dan Arja Lee.

Tak ada apa lagi yang hendak dipertahankan. Tiya memujuk sungguh-sungguh dan beri harapan pada Black yang dia tetap akan tunggu Black sampai hujung nyawa.

programme.title: Heart Attack
programme.desc: "Yoon, seorang pereka grafik bebas berusia 30 tahun, terkenal dengan etika kerjanya yang ekstrem. Dia sanggup bekerja tanpa tidur selama berhari-hari demi memenuhi tarikh akhir projek. Gaya hidup ini menyebabkan kesihatannya merosot, dan dia mula mengalami ruam misteri di seluruh badan.(Tumblr) Yoon mendapatkan rawatan daripada Dr. Imm, seorang pakar dermatologi muda yang berdedikasi. Kunjungan berkala ke klinik dan interaksi dengan Dr. Imm menimbulkan perasaan cinta dalam diri Yoon. Namun, dia bergelut untuk menyatakan perasaannya kerana terikat dengan gaya hidup yang tidak sihat dan tekanan kerja yang berterusan.(The Knockturnal) Filem ini menggambarkan dilema Yoon antara mengejar kejayaan kerjaya dan menjaga kesihatan serta hubungan peribadi. Ia juga menyoroti bagaimana cinta dan perhatian boleh menjadi pemangkin untuk seseorang menilai semula keutamaan hidupnya."

programme.title: Ayahanda Ep13
programme.desc: Hj Abdullah menjelaskan kepada Mazni mengenai kisah masa lalu hubungan Aziz dengan Rahayu, hubungan mereka renggang akibat tindakannya melarang perhubungan tersebut. Aziz telah mengecewakannya kerana gagal mendapat ijazah. Mazni sedar dan insaf dengan tindakannya dan menerima kehadiran Rahayu sebagai madunya. Aziz telah memenangi peraduan Sayembara peringkat kebangsaan. Hj Abdullah bersama Aziz dan Azwan keluar memancing, tiba-tiba ribut kuat menyebabkan Aziz jatuh ke laut. Hj Abdullah terjun untuk menyelamatkan Aziz, menyebabkan dia hampir lemas. Pertama kali selepas 15 tahun, Aziz solat subuh bersama ahli keluarganya berimamkan bapanya, Hj Abdullah menyerahkan sebuah buku yang ditulis sendiri kepada Aziz. Sebenarnya bakat penulisan Hj Abdullah telah dianugerahkan kepada Aziz. Mereka akhirnya bersatu semula sebagai keluarga besar Imam Hj Abdullah.

programme.title: Dihatiku Ada Kamu Ep8
programme.desc: Pada tahun 2016, Adif ditemuduga oleh Idris untuk jawatan peguam syarikat,. Adif gembira diterima kerja. Idris memuji Adif dalam mesyuarat dan berkongsi tentang anaknya, Rian, yang bakal graduasi. Pada 2017, Adif menghadiri majlis perkahwinan Hafiz iaitu saudara mara Rian. Adif kemudian meyakinkan Ahli Lembaga tentang perubahan syarikat dan meminta , mendesak dris menandatangani dokumen pemindahan harta, dengan syarat Adif akan tidak menyakiti Rian. Ia kejutan besat buat Idris. Selepas menandatangani dokumen sebagai Penaung, Adif merasa dendamnya terbalas dengan meletakkan gambar keluarganya di pejabat Idris.

programme.desc: Seorang pemandu teksi menggunakan perkhidmatannya sebagai penyamaran untuk kegiatan pemerasan, dan apabila tingkah laku adiknya yang impulsif menarik perhatian polis dan kumpulan samseng ke ambang pintu mereka, dia sanggup melakukan apa sahaja demi melindungi orang-orang yang penting dalam hidupnya.

programme.title: Budak Pendamping
programme.desc: Ia mengisahkan tentang seorang budak yang berumur 16 tahun, bernama Firash. Dibesarkan sebagai seorang anak tunggal di sebuah keluarga yang sentiasa sibuk dengan kerjaya, membuatkan Firash lebih senang bersendiriaan. Disebabkan itu keluarganya membuat keputusan untuk hantarnya ke sebuah kem. Disana Firash bertembung dengan Idlan dan rakannya Khai dan Sahar, serta sebahagian dalam Ahli Majlis Tertinggi Asrama (AMTA) bagi kem tersebut. Akibat ketidakpuasan mereka terhadap Firash yang kelihatan lembik, badannya menjadi tempat untuk mereka lepaskan kekerasan. Namun kehadiran budak pendamping mengubah segalanya untuk Firash tetapi ia juga menggugat kesejahteraan yang dah lama tidak bergelora. Lantas, adakah perjanjian antara Firash dan pendampingnya merupakan ilusi semata - mata ataupun terdapat hutang yang akan dituntut antaranya dengan Tuan Daud?

programme.title: Losmen Melati Ep3
programme.desc: Di tengah-tengah suasana yang tidak menentu, Melati dan Golok dikejutkan dengan kedatangan tetamu luar biasa, Wewe Gombel, yang telah menghidu mangsanya di halaman Melati Inn. Ketika Melati dan Golok cuba mengejar dan menundukkannya, rahsia silam Melati terbongkar, akhirnya membawa Wewe Gombel untuk mencari apa yang dia cari.

programme.desc: Seorang lelaki dengan masa lalu yang penuh misteri melarikan diri ke luar negara untuk melepaskan diri daripada neraka peribadinya namun akhirnya tiba di sebuah tempat yang jauh lebih mengerikan.

programme.title: Gadis Hitam Putih
programme.desc: Kota Jakarta telah digemparkan dengan berita kejadian lebih 20 tahun lalu. Dalam satu perbicaraan di mahkamah, seorang jururawat bernama Mira mengaku telah menukar bayi dua keluarga yang mempunyai latar belakang yang berbeza. Mira bertindak sebegitu kerana dia ingin membalas dendam terhadap seorang doktor yang memutuskan cintanya kerana perbezaan darjat keturunan.

programme.title: Ilhamku
programme.desc: Sham, seorang lelaki weirdo yang kreatif dan gemar menghadapi cabaran, bersetuju menjadi juri bagi sebuah uji bakat atas permintaan sahabatnya, Shima. Di situlah dia bertemu dengan Noreen, seorang penyanyi baharu yang berbakat namun bermasalah. Meskipun Noreen sering menimbulkan pelbagai masalah di syarikat rakaman kerana sikap tidak berdisiplinnya, Sham yang jatuh hati padanya sentiasa memaafkan segala kesilapannya. Namun, kasih sayang tanpa batas itu akhirnya memakan diri apabila Noreen semakin angkuh dan mula mempergunakan Sham demi kepentingan peribadinya.

programme.title: Sayang
programme.desc: Pelajar kolej swasta, Noni sering dikawal ketat oleh abangnya, Herman dan tidak boleh keluar bersosial seperti temannya yang lain. Herman mula bertindak menjadi ketua keluarga setelah kematian bapa mereka setahun yang lalu. Noni menghadiri satu majlis hari jadi dan terjadi sesuatu yang membuatkan Herman semakin ketat mengawal gerak geri Noni.

programme.title: Kemarau Panjang
programme.desc: Berlatarbelakangkan zaman darurat 19481960, Kampung Hulu menjadi sasaran ancaman komunis yang semakin menggugat keamanan penduduk. Demi mempertahankan keselamatan, pihak British berusaha menubuhkan pasukan Home Guard. Namun, dalam kekalutan yang melanda, muncul beberapa pengkhianat yang menjadi tali barut komunis, lantas mencetuskan kekacauan dan ketegangan yang kian meruncing dalam komuniti kampung itu.

programme.title: Da Di Du
programme.desc: Badu, Badi dan Bada, bertemu dan menjadi sahabat ketika mempelajari ilmu persilatan dengan seorang guru persilatan bernama Pak Tua kerana ingin memperbetulkan kisah silam yang tidak menyebelahi nasib mereka. Sepanjang itu terdapat pelbagai peristiwa yang berlaku dari mula mereka belajar sehingga tamat dan pulang ke kampung masing-masing untuk memperbetulkan masa lalu mereka.

programme.title: Teruna Idaman
programme.desc: Leha, seorang gadis lincah dan berdikari, sering menolak pinangan yang diatur ibunya. Alasannya mudah dia belum bersedia dan belum bertemu jejaka idaman. Setiap kali ada rombongan merisik, Leha rela berpura-pura kurang siuman semata-mata mahu menggagalkan rancangan perkahwinan itu. Namun, segalanya berubah apabila Tengku Iskandar, seorang pegawai baharu yang kacak dan berkarisma, muncul di tempat kerjanya. Buat pertama kali, hati Leha mula terusik. Demi menarik perhatian Iskandar, Leha sanggup lakukan apa saja termasuk mengorbankan wang simpanannya. Tapi adakah cinta berbalas, atau sekadar angan-angan?

programme.title: Sayang Salmah
programme.desc: Semangat cinta akan bangsa dan negara diterapkan dalam diri Hassan dan Salleh selaku anak kepada Encik Jabar dan Dasimah yang inginkan anak mereka mempunyai rasa patriotik akan negara. Hassan, aktif dalam bidang politik manakala Salleh menjadi seorang pemuda liar yang suka berhibur. Segalanya berubah apabila ayah mereka meninggal dunia.

programme.title: Merah
programme.desc: Pilihan antara baik atau buruk menentukan di mana pengakhiran jalan kisah hidup Merah. Terpaksa menjalani hukuman penjara akibat pilihan yang dibuatnya, Merah bertemu seseorang yang istimewa. Kasih, seorang kaunselor menemui Merah. Namun, ada rahsia yang disimpan erat oleh Kasih. Meskipun menyukai antara satu sama lain, pelbagai halangan terpaksa mereka tempuhi bersama.

programme.title: Penghujung Jalan
programme.desc: Mastura, seorang wanita muda yang terlanjur cinta, terpaksa menanggung akibat apabila hamil luar nikah. Selepas melahirkan, dia nekad meninggalkan bayinya di hadapan rumah Aina dan Rosli, pasangan suami isteri yang masih meratapi kehilangan anak akibat keguguran. Kehadiran bayi itu seolah-olah menghidupkan semula harapan mereka untuk menjadi ibu bapa. Namun, apabila pihak berkuasa campur tangan demi siasatan, bayi itu terpaksa diambil semula. Hal ini meninggalkan Aina dalam kesedihan yang mendalam, sekali lagi kehilangan sesuatu yang sangat berharga.

programme.desc: Kota Jakarta telah digemparkan dengan berita kejadian lebih 20 tahun lalu. Dalam satu perbicaraan di mahkamah, seorang jururawat bernama Mira mengaku telah menukar bayi dua keluarga yang mempunyai latar belakang yang berbeza. Mira bertindak sebegitu kerana dia ingin membalas dendam terhadap seorang doktor yang memutuskan cintanya kerana perbezaan darjat keturunan.

programme.title: Namaku Yassin
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Yanto, seorang penjual jagung bakar yang menjalani kehidupan sederhana di kampung. Segalanya berubah apabila dia bertemu semula dengan sahabat lamanya, Budi, yang baru pulang setelah beberapa tahun bekerja di Malaysia. Terkesima dengan kejayaan Budi, Yanto menerima pelawaan untuk turut sama mengubah nasibnya di Kuala Lumpur. Menggunakan nama samaran "Yassin", dia bekerja sebagai buruh di tapak pembinaan dan bersahabat dengan Mahmud. Di sebalik cabaran hidup di kota, Yassin turut menemui cinta dalam diri Liza, seorang pengurus di tempat kerjanya. Namun, perjalanan mencari rezeki dan erti kehidupan ini tidak semudah yang disangka.

programme.title: Sayang
programme.desc: Pelajar kolej swasta, Noni sering dikawal ketat oleh abangnya, Herman dan tidak boleh keluar bersosial seperti temannya yang lain. Herman mula bertindak menjadi ketua keluarga setelah kematian bapa mereka setahun yang lalu. Noni menghadiri satu majlis hari jadi dan terjadi sesuatu yang membuatkan Herman semakin ketat mengawal gerak geri Noni.

programme.title: Ilhamku
programme.desc: Sham, seorang lelaki weirdo yang kreatif dan gemar menghadapi cabaran, bersetuju menjadi juri bagi sebuah uji bakat atas permintaan sahabatnya, Shima. Di situlah dia bertemu dengan Noreen, seorang penyanyi baharu yang berbakat namun bermasalah. Meskipun Noreen sering menimbulkan pelbagai masalah di syarikat rakaman kerana sikap tidak berdisiplinnya, Sham yang jatuh hati padanya sentiasa memaafkan segala kesilapannya. Namun, kasih sayang tanpa batas itu akhirnya memakan diri apabila Noreen semakin angkuh dan mula mempergunakan Sham demi kepentingan peribadinya.

programme.title: Da Di Du
programme.desc: Badu, Badi dan Bada, bertemu dan menjadi sahabat ketika mempelajari ilmu persilatan dengan seorang guru persilatan bernama Pak Tua kerana ingin memperbetulkan kisah silam yang tidak menyebelahi nasib mereka. Sepanjang itu terdapat pelbagai peristiwa yang berlaku dari mula mereka belajar sehingga tamat dan pulang ke kampung masing-masing untuk memperbetulkan masa lalu mereka.

programme.title: Kemarau Panjang
programme.desc: Berlatarbelakangkan zaman darurat 19481960, Kampung Hulu menjadi sasaran ancaman komunis yang semakin menggugat keamanan penduduk. Demi mempertahankan keselamatan, pihak British berusaha menubuhkan pasukan Home Guard. Namun, dalam kekalutan yang melanda, muncul beberapa pengkhianat yang menjadi tali barut komunis, lantas mencetuskan kekacauan dan ketegangan yang kian meruncing dalam komuniti kampung itu.

programme.title: Sayang Salmah
programme.desc: Semangat cinta akan bangsa dan negara diterapkan dalam diri Hassan dan Salleh selaku anak kepada Encik Jabar dan Dasimah yang inginkan anak mereka mempunyai rasa patriotik akan negara. Hassan, aktif dalam bidang politik manakala Salleh menjadi seorang pemuda liar yang suka berhibur. Segalanya berubah apabila ayah mereka meninggal dunia.

programme.title: Teruna Idaman
programme.desc: Leha, seorang gadis lincah dan berdikari, sering menolak pinangan yang diatur ibunya. Alasannya mudah dia belum bersedia dan belum bertemu jejaka idaman. Setiap kali ada rombongan merisik, Leha rela berpura-pura kurang siuman semata-mata mahu menggagalkan rancangan perkahwinan itu. Namun, segalanya berubah apabila Tengku Iskandar, seorang pegawai baharu yang kacak dan berkarisma, muncul di tempat kerjanya. Buat pertama kali, hati Leha mula terusik. Demi menarik perhatian Iskandar, Leha sanggup lakukan apa saja termasuk mengorbankan wang simpanannya. Tapi adakah cinta berbalas, atau sekadar angan-angan?

programme.title: Merah
programme.desc: Pilihan antara baik atau buruk menentukan di mana pengakhiran jalan kisah hidup Merah. programme.desc: Mastura, seorang wanita muda yang terlanjur cinta, terpaksa menanggung akibat apabila hamil luar nikah. programme.title: Pertiwiku Ep1

programme.title: Bujang Berani S2 Ep3

programme.title: Cincin Pusaka
programme.desc: Alina dan Sofian adalah dua beradik yang saling cemburu, berlumba mengalahkan satu sama lain sejak kecil. Setelah kematian nenek, mereka berebut untuk memiliki cincin pusaka nenek yang kononnya mempunyai magis tertentu. Tetapi pelbagai halangan terjadi untuk mereka mewarisinya. Mampukah mereka menghadapi segala rintangan demi sebentuk cincin pusaka?

programme.title: Sejoli
programme.desc: Jo (Bront Palarae) dan Gina (Maya Karin) sedang menyembuhkan hati yang terluka di Phuket apabila takdir mempertemukan mereka. Pada mulanya mereka saling membenci, tetapi apabila mereka mendapat tahu bahawa bekas kekasih masing-masing, Hardy (Remy Ishak) dan Nita (Izara Aishah), akan berkahwin, mereka merancang untuk menggagalkan majlis perkahwinan tersebut.

programme.title: Reaksiar Ep2
programme.desc: Program yang memaparkan perkongsian pengalaman dan reaksi artis-artis jemputan setelah melihat kembali klip-klip lakonan mereka.

programme.title: Taikun
programme.desc: Mengisahkan dua lelaki bernama Tai dan Kun, sahabat baik yang hanya meminati pergaduhan dan mencuri. Apabila tabiat buruk mereka menyebabkan mereka bertembung dan memukul teruk ahli geng Pink dan Purple, Tai dan Kun kemudian direkrut oleh ketua geng yang kagum dengan kemahiran mereka.

programme.title: Gerabak Cinta
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Luna, usahawan berjaya yang ditipu tunangnya, Razi. Dia kecewa apabila perniagaan yang mereka usahakan rugi kerana Razi terbabit dengan skandal wang serta mempunyai perempuan simpanan. Sementara itu, Gie pula baru saja dibuang kerja. Walaupun masih mencari kerja, dia sangat tenang dan tetap ceria. Gie reda dengan situasi menimpanya.

programme.title: Nada Siar Ep46
programme.desc: Sebuah program yang menyajikan kepada anda klip-klip video soundtrack yang terkandung dalam filem-filem klasik tempatan.

programme.title: Misteri Mary Kuale
programme.desc: Aileena sebenarnya anak angkat kepada Puan Katrina dan Tuan Haidar. Mereka menemui Aileena di dalam sebuah kotak yang ditinggalkan di tepi tong sampah. Pada masa tersebut, Puan Katrina dan Tuan Haidar baru dua tahun berkahwin. Melihat sahaja bayi perempuan yang comel itu, Puan Katrina langsung jatuh kasih dan meminta izin kepada suaminya untuk menjaga bayi itu. Aileena sentiasa didatangi mimpi mengenai seorang wanita gila berketurunan cina . Dalam mimpinya itu Aileena dipanggil anak dan dia sentiasa melarikan diri daripada wanita itu. adakah maksud tersirat disebalik mimpi itu?

programme.title: Adnan Sempit 2
programme.desc: Adnan, seorang penunggang motosikal jalanan yatim piatu yang dijaga oleh ibu saudaranya. Sebaliknya, Nadia dilahirkan dalam keluarga kaya dan kini memiliki pekerjaan yang stabil. Kedua-dua insan yang berbeza ini bertemu secara kebetulan dan akhirnya menjalin hubungan. Kini, dalam "Adnan Sempit 2", Shaheizy Sam kembali memegang watak sebagai Adnan, mengisahkan cabaran dan dugaan dalam kehidupannya serta hubungannya dengan Nadia.

programme.title: Abang Long Fadil
programme.desc: Abang Long Fadil, seorang lelaki yang sentiasa berangan bahawa kehidupannya seperti seorang gangster. Tetapi apabila sahabat baiknya, Malik dimasukkan ke penjara, lebih banyak kekacauan berlaku dan angan-angannya mungkin tidak jauh berbeza daripada realiti.

programme.title: Taikun
programme.desc: Mengisahkan dua lelaki bernama Tai dan Kun, sahabat baik yang hanya meminati pergaduhan dan mencuri. programme.title: Nana dan Jam Atok
programme.desc: Kisah tentang Nana dikenali sebagai seorang pelajar yang pemalas dan sering lewat ke sekolah. Alasan yang sering digunakan adalah jam di rumahnya rosak dan tidak berbunyi. Puas ayahnya menukar jam dibilik Nana dengan harapan ada perubahan.

programme.title: Sampai 7 Keturunan
programme.desc: Dalam satu peraduan cabutan bertuah, Aidil telah terpilih untuk memenangi percutian lima hari empat malam di sebuah hotel lima bintang serta wang tunai sebanyak lima ribu ringgit. Namun begitu, disebabkan isterinya Syikin yang sedang hamil, Aidil memutuskan untuk tidak mengambil percutian tersebut. Walaupun begitu, Aidil berasa sayang untuk melepaskan hadiah itu begitu sahaja. Dia memberikan wang tunai dan tiket tersebut kepada Pak Karim, yang pada mulanya keberatan untuk menerimanya kerana bimbang meninggalkan ayam kesayangannya. Setelah dipujuk berkali-kali, Pak Karim akhirnya bersetuju walaupun masih risaukan ayamnya.

programme.title: Jika Fattah
programme.desc: Kehadiran Fattah yang merupakan seorang anak yatim di dalam keluarga Zaidi telah mengubah kehidupan mereka sekeluarga melalui sikap terpuji yang ada di dalam diri Fattah yang menyedarkan Zaidi dan isterinya Intan.

programme.title: AKSI Indonesia Ep16
programme.desc: 24 Ustaz dan Ustazah dari pelbagai wilayah di Indonesia mengambil langkah untuk menang dengan melibatkan diri dalam pelbagai aktiviti Islamik yang menghiburkan dan bermakna. Saksikan dakwah mereka beraksi bersama para pengulas.

programme.title: Indahnya Kebersamaan Ep31
programme.desc: Indahnya Kebersamaan ialah sebuah program tausiah yang dikendalikan oleh Mellya Baskarani bersama Prof. Dr. K.H. Nasaruddin Umar, M.A. Program ini memberi fokus kepada pelbagai permasalahan yang sering dialami oleh masyarakat, termasuk isu dalam kehidupan berumah tangga.

programme.title: Temanku Adalah Maut Dalam Pernikahanku
programme.desc: Tari dan Andre adalah pasangan suami isteri yang bahagia. Namun, kedatangan sahabat Tari menyebabkan masalah dan konflik dalam rumah tangga mereka. Persahabatan itu mula mengancam kebahagiaan rumah tangga mereka.

programme.title: Superstar Junior S1 Ep2
programme.desc: Superstar Junior Indonesia ialah pertandingan bakat kanak-kanak yang disiarkan di Mentari TV. Rancangan ini menampilkan peserta cilik dari seluruh negara yang menunjukkan bakat dalam nyanyian, tarian dan lakonan untuk memikat hati juri dan penonton.

programme.title: Doyan Makan Ep4
programme.desc: Doyan Makan menjemput penonton untuk mengikuti perjalanan dan pengalaman kulinari untuk makanan popular di kawasan tersebut, serta akan meninjau informasi tentang tempat, harga dan proses penghasilan makanan yang mereka nikmati.

programme.title: The Tradition Story of Taiwan (T) Ep5134
programme.desc: The Tradition Story of Taiwan presents a series of tales and folktales in Taiwan that have been pass down from one generation to another generation.

programme.title: Wish Comes True
programme.desc: Xiao Fei is a cheerful girl who has been abandoned by her mother. One day, she encounters a gifted young man named Zi Wai, who is battling a rare disease. Determined to help him, she embarks on a journey to find his lost love. Even when they discover that the drug treating Wai is ineffective, they choose to embrace hope and love together.

programme.title: Mission Milano
programme.desc: A wealthy entrepreneur goes undercover with an Interpol agent to protect a new invention, the Seed of God, from falling into an international crime conglomerate.

programme.title: YUM Investigation
programme.desc: YUM is a detective agency that handles supernatural cases. As YUM investigates the evil spirits appearing in an old building, they discover that the spirits are created by a spirit master to haunt the residents so that the building can be vacated for redevelopment. Can the YUM investigators finally find ways to fight against the master?

programme.title: Romantic Dream
programme.desc: Dino meets his dream girl Mandy and falls in love with her at first sight. However, she disappears suddenly and he only sees her again after nine years, when she is already married. To overcome the pain of losing his love, Dino finds a guru with supernatural power to make him meet Mandy in his dream.

programme.title: Last Suspect
programme.desc: Lawyer Chen receives a mysterious call demanding her to defend a murder suspect after her daughter is kidnapped, and is told that she can only save her daughter by winning the case. As she starts investigation with the police and evidence emerges, Chen discovers the truth and reveals the mastermind. Can she rescue her daughter in time?

programme.title: My Wife is a Gambling Maestro
programme.desc: Natalie Yao Meng stars as the gambling queen, Ying Ying, who is a contender for the Asian God of Gamblers competition. But before the competition she is betrayed by her fianc and left for dead. Rescued by a young man called Gerrard, who suffering from amnesia, Ying Ying, must recover in time to compete in the big event!

programme.title: Young Ip Man: Crisis Time
programme.desc: Set in 1917, young Ip Man pursues his studies in Hong Kong. The school is held hostage on the day of an English speech competition, and as Ip Man decides to step up and fight the crisis, it is revealed that his master and his childhood friend are behind all this. Can he take them down and uphold justice?

programme.title: Better Days
programme.desc: In this Oscar nominee for Best International Feature Film, Nian faces relentless bullying from her peers as she prepares for her college entrance exam. Fate leads her to streetwise punk Bei, but before they can retreat into their own world, both are embroiled in a murder investigation that will change their lives forever.

programme.title: Find Your Voice
programme.desc: The passion choir pilot program trains students from three underperforming schools choir to participate in an inter-school choral competition. While it seems impossible, a renowned conductor, Yim Tsz Long, unexpectedly agrees to lead the choir. Will the passion choir and Maestro Yim complete this impossible mission and win the competition?

programme.title: Sex and the Beauties
programme.desc: It is said that Hong Kong is a sexy and sexual city where life is breathtakingly fast but glamorous. Fear of marriage, single & successful psychiatrist, Selina and other beauties seek for love and happy endings.

programme.title: Call Me Agent
programme.desc: Miu Ling dreams of becoming a secret agent. Even though it seems impossible, she still harbours such a dream and hopes that it will soon come true. One day, Miu Ling rescues an injured secret agent who promises to make her his apprentice. From then on, her life is turned upside down and she goes onto a roller-coaster of madcap adventures.

programme.title: Break Up Club
programme.desc: Joe is a 20-something slacker who only takes one thing seriously: his on-and-off girlfriend Flora. After their latest breakup, Joe goes to an audition for a documentary by director Barbara Wong. Handed a camera, Joe records his discovery of a magical website that reunites him with Flora at the price of breaking up his best friend and his girlfriend. However, despite the efficiency of the website, Joe's refusal to change his immature ways and Flora's attraction to a talented graffiti artist threatens to break them up once more.

programme.title: Inner Senses
programme.desc: Haunted by recurring visions stemming from past traumas, Yan reaches out to psychiatrist Dr Jim to restore her sanity and overcome her troubled past. Yet, as Yan gradually heals, Jim finds himself haunted by the same disturbing images, as his suppressed memories resurface.

programme.title: Saving General Yang
programme.desc: The Khitan army takes revenge for a past massacre by abducting General Yang Ye and setting up a deadly trap for the seven Yang brothers. Led by the eldest son, the seven brothers set out with a small band of fighters to bring their father home.

programme.title: Band Four
programme.desc: An aspiring singer of an indie band called Band Four reunites with her estranged guitarist father following the death of her mother. Together with her half-sister and her nine-year-old son, the newly reunited family come together to support each other through their love and passion for music.

programme.title: Nezha
programme.desc: A former top team racing driver wants to prove himself in a race but accidentally hurts his teammate Lily, leading to the teams downfall. When an inexperienced virtual car racing champion joins the team and unexpectedly shines in a real-life race, can the three drivers team up to regain glory for their team?

programme.title: Far Far Away
programme.desc: A 28-year-old IT geek has only been in love once. Surprisingly, he ends up getting romantically involved with five different women this year and the one thing they have in common is that they all live in far flung areas of Hong Kong. After taking five intensive relationship courses within these 365 days, will he find the-one?

programme.title: Chasing the Dragon
programme.desc: Infamous real-life drug kingpin Crippled Ho came to Hong Kong as an illegal immigrant in 1963 and ruthlessly built an empire from the chaotic underworld of drug dealers and corrupt police who ruled the city under notorious detective Lee Rock.

programme.title: Hero
programme.desc: Set in 2020 during the outbreak of COVID-19, the movie features interconnected stories of three women's lives as they navigate the uncertain future amongst their respective friends and families. From the struggles at home to challenges in relationships and conflicts at work, these three women rise with strength when faced with plights unknown.

programme.title: The Eye
programme.desc: Mun undergoes a cornea transplant to correct her blindness, but ends up gaining more than the gift of sight. She shockingly realises that she is seeing another woman instead of herself whenever she looks into a mirror. Recalling that things changed ever since her cornea was replaced, Mun vows to uncover the truth behind her strange vision

programme.title: Love Lies
programme.desc: Gynaecologist Veronica downloads a dating app for fun. Little does she know that the charming French engineer on the other end is actually a local con artist named Joe, who is a member of an online scam group. As their fake relationship unfolds, both Joes guilty conscience and Veronicas hopes intensify.

programme.title: Cyber Heist
programme.desc: Hackers have caused a large-scale cyber attack, but luckily cyber security engineer Chun, manages to fend it off with his protective firewall system. To Chun's surprise, his boss is the mastermind of the attack, and when Chun gets trapped in a money laundering operation, he must fight against his boss in the cyber world to prove his innocence.

programme.title: I Believe
programme.desc: Chu Chu has been waiting for her first love for 10 years but he marries someone else in the end. As she loses faith in love, she meets a wedding planner and a handsome and rich man, who both help her get over her ex-boyfriend. As Chu Chu feels the same love from them, she must make up her mind. Who will she choose in the end?

programme.title: Cliff Walkers
programme.desc: The first spy thriller movie by famous Director Zhang Yi Mou, this film follows four Communist Party special agents who embark on a secret operation in the Japanese puppet state of Manchukuo in 1932. Sold out by a traitor, the agents, who split up into two teams, find themselves surrounded by threats on all sides. Can they complete their mission?

programme.title: Fight Back to School
programme.desc: The number one killer in SDU, Chow Sing Sing(Stephen Chow), is sent to a school to find a lost gun. His partner Tat(Ng Man Tat) pretends to be a school worker in assisting him. They recognize that some students are being closed with Fei, the head of triad society, and Fei traffics munitions. Sing steals and ignites Fei's munitions; Fei pledges to kill Sing...

programme.title: Hidden Heroine
programme.desc: A drug cartel is entrenched in the Dong Zhou area. Mei Jing of the Thunderbolt Womens Commando Unit, leads her team to attack the drug base, but they are being ambushed and the identity of Meis father as an undercover is exposed. After a fierce battle, Mei and her team manage to successfully defeat the drug cartel and rescue her father.

programme.title: Beauty And The 7 Beasts
programme.desc: Teddy, once a renowned movie star, is facing a career decline. To make a living, he accepts five disciples to shape them into stars. Teddys career regains momentum after he reunites with his long-lost daughter, but he is also confronted by a rival at the same time. His daughter and disciples decide to help him overcome this difficult situation

programme.title: Shadows
programme.desc: Ching is a forensic psychiatrist who has the power to enter a persons subconscious mind. In her latest case, she suspects that another psychiatrist is responsible for a brutal murder-cum-suicide case involving a social worker. In the investigation process, Ching finds herself under suspicion instead, as she comes face-to-face with a past trauma

programme.title: Infernal Affairs III
programme.desc: Ming is transferred to do menial police work ten months after the murder of Yan, in 2004. Meanwhile, a new star, Wing, has emerged in the police force and Ming suspects he is also a mole sent by the triad. Determined to start anew, Ming must kill Wing while ensuring his own identity does not get exposed.

programme.title: Wo Hu
programme.desc: The Hong Kong Police has placed more than a thousand undercover officers in various triad groups to bring down the largest criminal organization in Hong Kong. Betrayal, deceit and murder bring this group of "brothers" into a collision with the law and with each other!

programme.title: Silent Code
programme.desc: Reporter Lan is tasked to research news from the internet, and stumbles across a popular BBS forum, Dream Board. The forum founder Xiang, creates space for netizens to share dreams and ideas, but ends up being the subject of a heated debate due to a leaked video. As Lan digs for the truth, she finds that things more complicated than they seem...

programme.title: Infernal Affairs
programme.desc: Yan is a police mole in the triad and joined them before he graduated from the police academy, while Ming is a triad mole in the police since young. Leading parallel lives, both men feel increasingly trapped in their false surroundings, and a series of cat-and-mouse chases ensue as both the triad and the police compete to uncover the others mole.

programme.title: Wish Comes True
programme.desc: Xiao Fei is a cheerful girl who has been abandoned by her mother. One day, she encounters a gifted young man named Zi Wai, who is battling a rare disease. Determined to help him, she embarks on a journey to find his lost love. Even when they discover that the drug treating Wai is ineffective, they choose to embrace hope and love together.

programme.title: The Lark
programme.desc: Sixties pop star Carrie Ku plays the "Little Lark" in this romantic-drama of mistaken identity that is a treasure trove of some of the most popular Mandarin songs of all time.

programme.title: Super Inframan
programme.desc: Transformed from a young laboratory researcher, the thunderbolt-fisted Inframan must battle Princess Dragon Mom who wakes up from hibernation to conquer the earth with her army of mutant monsters.

programme.title: Fangs of the Cobra
programme.desc: Incredibly, the title serpent is not a harbinger of horror, but actually the film's hero. This virtuous viper sniffs out bombs, fights gangs, battles a baby-killing rodent and even takes on a duplicitous woman. This one-of-a-kind thriller will be applauded by reptile fans everywhere.

programme.title: Call to Arms
programme.desc: The aggressive and dangerous Chin Empire conquers the hard-put Chao kingdom while the Wei empire is drained of its heroes and paralyzed by an indecisive ruler. Adventure, intrigue, death and tragedy reigns before the triumphant clash of the armies.

programme.title: The 5 Billion Dollar Legacy
programme.desc: A crippled billionaire mails a letter to each of his long-lost daughters inviting them to go to Japan, in the hope that he will find a worthy heir to inherit his vast fortune. The sisters finally meet abroad the plane to Japan, and one of them is taken with a man who is going to investigate the death of his lawyer uncle in a mysterious hit-and-run.

programme.title: Mission Impossible
programme.desc: A sword masters daughter is pursued and poisoned by an evil master when bringing back the stolen Golden Sword to the palace. She dies on the run and returns as a spirit to take revenge by killing the evil master, and soon vanishes after returning the sword to the emperor.

programme.title: Moonlight Serenade
programme.desc: A sweet inn-keepers daughter is witness to a perverted rape, leading to more danger than most romantic dramas can handle. Can her true love rescue her in time? For this movie, the moonlight serenade is the sound of suspense, leading to more danger than most romantic dramas can handle.

programme.title: The Bloody Escape
programme.desc: Ku is a skilled Kung Fu artist brought up by the bandits and does not agree with the brutal leader of the bandits camp. He rescues Tong, a young lady forced to become the leaders wife, causing both the authorities and bandits to come after them. Ku has to stand up against the bandits that he grew up with so as to start a new life for himself.

programme.title: Hex
programme.desc: This supernatural mystery tells the story of a sickly wife and her maid conspiring to kill her beastly husband, leading to a string of events with spooky twists and turns.

programme.title: Clan of Amazons
programme.desc: The martial arts world is plunged into terror when a mysterious figure known as the 'Embroidery Bandit' starts to attack convoys of precious materials. Seemingly unstoppable, the frightened clans decide to call on the expertise of Lu Xiao Feng, an inquisitive fighter and detective to capture the culprit.

programme.title: The Bells of Death
programme.desc: Wei Fu is an unremarkable woodcutter. However, when psychotic marauders killed his family and abducted his sister, he goes through vigorous martial arts training with an expert swordsman in order to exact revenge on the evildoers.

programme.title: Disciples Of Shaolin
programme.desc: Yi is a skilled disciple of the Hong Quan style kung fu who work in a textile mill recommended by his senior, Han. Han warns Yi not to show off his martial arts skill so as to avoid getting into trouble. However, Yi does not listen and eventually gets dangerously involved in the conflict between two opposing textile mills.

programme.title: A Taste Of Cold Steel
programme.desc: Gan Dai Xiong is killed by Prince Wu, who seeks to seize his Purple Sword. Prince Wus son join forces with an evil gang to steal the Purple Sword from Gan Dai Xiongs three daughters. Eventually, Gans daughters team up with their cousin Xu to avenge their fathers death.

programme.title: Na Cha the Great
programme.desc: Adapted from a chapter of the classic Chinese legend Investiture of the Gods, this is the story of Na Cha set 3000 years ago. After Na Cha sacrificed his life to save his parents, he is reincarnated with his spirit embodied in a lotus flower and is armed with two magic weapons to save the people from their despotic emperor.

programme.title: Return to the 36th Chamber
programme.desc: The second film of the trilogy, Gordon Liu plays Zhou Ren Jie, a man who impersonates a monk in order to learn kung fu in Shaolin, and eventually creates his own Shaolin style of scaffolding kung fu.

programme.title: Carry on Doctors and Nurses
programme.desc: At St. Morant Hospital, a harried but lovely administrator must deal with lusty interns, student nurses, a delirious surgeon, a dissection fiend, a criticizing Commissioner and gross negligence at regular intervals! This comedy is based on the hugely successful British Carry On! film series.

programme.title: The Magnificent Ruffians
programme.desc: A gang of unemployed martial artists seem to have their bad fortunes turned when the head of a local security agency hires them to take out the competition, who their new employer insists is up to no good. However, the men are being played for fools and have to take each other on until the last drop of blood is spilled.

programme.title: Till the End of Time
programme.desc: This is Jenny Hu's stunning debut as a struggling singer who tries to keep her career and marriage intact. This movie also includes seven memorable hit songs.

programme.title: Shaolin Mantis
programme.desc: The Emperor orders Feng to find proofs of Master Tians rebellion in his house. Feng falls in love with Tians granddaughter and marries her. When he finds the proofs and tries to leave with her, his wife is killed in the fight against Tian. Feng creates the mantis-style martial arts and vows to avenge her death.

programme.title: Tragic Commitment
programme.desc: When the husband of a doctor, Tung is fatally wounded in an accident, he reveals to her about his affair with Blackie, who is impregnated with his baby. Despite the devastation of the betrayal and the eventual death of her husband, Tung is pressured by her mother-in-law into putting up with Blackie and offer $1M for her baby...

programme.title: Twelve Deadly Coins
programme.desc: When Qiao Miao is about to kill the bandit whom he just met, he is attracted by her beauty and they quickly fall in love. The two later discover the blood feud between the owner of the unique weapon - Twelve Deadly Coins and the old master who controls the bandit...

programme.title: The Mirror and the Lichee
programme.desc: The curious title in this Huangmei Opera romance refers to the two props that signal a happy beginning between a scholar and a local beauty. The scholar polishes mirrors so as to be closer to his love, who signals her approval by tossing him some lichees. From that point on the course of their love becomes rocky, complete with murder and suicide.

programme.title: The Convict Killer
programme.desc: After spending fifteen years in prison on trumped-up charges for drug smuggling, the martial arts master Teng Piao embarks on a journey to take revenge on the person who sets him up - Black Leopard. Unfortunately for Piao, no one knows the real identity of Black Leopard, except that there is a black leopard tattoo on his chest.

programme.title: King Drummer
programme.desc: A young musician Chi Chiang is hired by the manager of a popular band when the group's drummer/leader Charlie, quits to join a rival group. The new drummer becomes an immediate hit, causing Charlie to be very jealous. Furthermore, the young drummer's mother is dead set against him having a music career.

programme.title: Raw Passions
programme.desc: Mrs Lin's husband and his friend both have affairs with a belly dancer Sasa, and are both blackmailed by her. Sasa is stabbed one day and her brother shows up asking for money. A mysterious man also claims he can offer evidence for cash to help Lins husband. Lin has to unveil the deceit, double-crosses and blackmailing before she is in danger too!

programme.title: The Casino
programme.desc: After being separated for many years, two childhood lovers meet in a possibly mythical "Lucky Casino" and vow to rid the establishment of the corrupt military generals, criminals and extortionists!

programme.title: The Female Prince
programme.desc: Hsiao's stepmother frames her fianc Lung when he refuses to forfeit their engagement and sends him to prison. To save him, Hsiao disguises as Lung to take the Imperial exam and ranks first place. Impressed by Hsiao, the Emperor weds the Princess to 'him'. When Hsiao comes clean on their wedding night, she persuades the Princess to follow a plan

programme.title: Killer Clans
programme.desc: This intriguing wuxia saga is packed with conspiracies, power schemes and sword fights to produce a perfect blend of great action and gripping drama. The movie centres around the struggle for underworld supremacy between two clans, where the line between good and evil is not always that clear-cut.

programme.title: Return of the Crazy Bumpkins
programme.desc: This sequel makes for more bittersweet laughs and heart-wrenching misfortune, as Ah Niu gets out of the jail to find his true love becoming the wife of an abusive husband, and his uncle further exploits his naive nature.

programme.title: Shaolin Hand Lock
programme.desc: Li Cheng Yings father was set up and killed by his old friend Ling Hao. Li, who has learnt Shaolin Hand Lock from his father, is on a mission to avenge his death. He works as an undercover guard at Lings house where he meets his long-lost brother, and the two team up to take revenge for their father against Ling.

programme.title: Mr. Funnybone Strikes Again
programme.desc: In this hilarious sequel, Mr Big Potato opens an old-fashioned Chinese clinic, but his traditional methods are rejected by the sceptics of modern Hong Kong. Enter his buddy Mr Funny bone to rescue his business!

programme.title: The Boxer From The Temple
programme.desc: A young monk, The Kid, was expelled from the temple due to his crazy ways. After leaving the temple, he fights a cruel bandit's son and befriends a prostitute. As he fights for justice, his Crazy Lo Han Fist improves with every fight.

programme.title: The Heroic Ones
programme.desc: Set in the Tang Dynasty, the 13 adopted sons of Sha Tuo King are all renowned as royal warriors. David Chiang plays the 13th Prince, a powerful fighter whose prestigious status provokes jealously, leading to a gruesome family feud.

programme.title: The Pure and the Evil
programme.desc: Two teen girls, Rose and May, become close friends despite their different social backgrounds. The rich girl May moves to America but returns years later to see Rose, now a beauty queen and bar girl. Rose is immediately attracted to Fangs fianc and their relationship quickly deteriorates when Rose sets out to pursue him

programme.title: Lady General Hua Mu-Lan
programme.desc: Mulan disguises herself as a male soldier to replace her aged father in a war against the barbarians. Her courage brings her victory in battles and she was promoted to a general. When Mulan returns home with glory, the chief commander asks her to marry his daughter, forcing Mulan to reveal her true identity.

programme.desc: She Said, She Said / Starfish - When one of Rikkis plants won't sing, Pixie and Juniper both tell their varying recollections of why the plant is suddenly silent. / Kelp, Scallop, and Cruz have always thought that starfish did nothing but laze about; but as they go about their day, the starfish goes through his own routine, completely unbeknownst to everyone else.

programme.title: Not Quite Narwhal Ep22
programme.desc: Leroys Caterpillar / Lost Spark - Leroy must learn to let go when his caterpillar friend turns into a butterfly. / When Pixie loses her spark, Kelp and Juniper look for the plant they think will cure her. Meanwhile Pixie wonders whether she can be cured at all!

programme.title: Spirit Riding Free Ep21
programme.desc: Lucky And The Impatient Patient - While Spirit recovers from his injuries, Lucky helps out at the soda shop.

programme.title: Spirit Riding Free Ep22
programme.desc: Lucky And The Train Tycoon - While Lucky is eager to celebrate her first birthday on the frontier, a surprise visit from her Grandpa stirs up a controversy.

programme.title: The Adventures Of Puss In Boots Ep21
programme.desc: Spell - As he tries to restore the magic spell that will protect San Lorenzo, Puss accidentally brings Artephius's macram owl shop to life.

programme.title: The Adventures Of Puss In Boots Ep22
programme.desc: Scimitar - While searching for items missing from the treasure house, Puss enlists the help of the Scimitar, an evil sword that turns its wielder wicked.

programme.title: The Epic Tales Of Captain Underpants Ep21
programme.desc: Captain Underpants and the Problematic Pandemonium of the Punishing Plungerina - After helping George and Harold make a comic featuring the heroine Plungerina, Erica asserts that Plungerina could be better that Captain Underpants. To prove her wrong, the boys decide to actually create the villain in the comic and then have Captain Underpants save the day. Unfortunately, Krupp - and therefore Captain Underpants - is away at a principals' convention.There's no one to save them...until a real life Plungerina saves tthe day! But who is really Plungerina?

programme.title: The Epic Tales Of Captain Underpants Ep22
programme.desc: Captain Underpants and the Bombastic Blathering of Brainy Blabulous - When Krupp transfers to another school, George and Harold follow, only to find a bizarro version of Jerome Horwitz Elementary, where the teachers are nice and the kids are well-behaved. But no one's having any fun! George and Harold want to right this wrong with pranks and comics. But Krupp enlists Mr. Neamer (bizarro Meaner), who then super-enlargers his brain and becomes Brainy Blabulous, in order to stop the subversion of authority.

programme.title: Go, Dog. Go! Ep11
programme.desc: Catch Me If You Sam / Toy Driver - Its Tag and Scoochs first day of Race Cadets and Sam Whippet tells the Cadets that whoever can catch him in a race will be the new team captain. \ When Mom donates a box of Tags old toys to the new daycare center, Tag decides that the only way to get her box of toys back is to go around town collecting toys to swap out for her toys.

programme.title: Not Quite Narwhal Ep11
programme.desc: Salty and Sweet / Cruz Blues - Chef J tells Ollie he cooks with love. Kelp and Ollie set out to make food with love for him. When various food combos fail, Ollie considers giving up, because it isnt good enough. Kelp goes to his Dad for answers, and two seemingly different ingredients form something magical. / When Cruz is not his usual upbeat self, Kelp tries various ways to cheer him up before realizing the best way to be a good friend is to just sit with him, and let him feel what hes feeling.

programme.title: Boss Baby: Back In Business Ep44
programme.desc: Chicago - Boss and family go on Spring Break to visit his grandparents in the big city of Chicago. Boss uses the trip to test his business mettle, by getting in a promotion war at a real big adult company. And when a department store refuses to let Gigi and Tim return an item, they wind up unionizing the entire sales force.

programme.title: Boss Baby: Back In Business Ep45
programme.desc: Baby Boss - Mom and Dad are panicking after Gigi noticed Boss isn't growing, so Boss "puts himself under", taking a special formula that will turn him int a regular baby long enough to pass a Doctor's checkup. However, with Boss gone, all the villains from this season see it as the perfect time to strike Baby Corp, leaving Staci to hold the floodgates.

programme.title: Boss Baby: Back In Business Ep46
programme.desc: Boom Baby - Looking to trim costs, Boss unknowingly fires Boom Baby, a super-undercover Baby Corp worker who displays to parents how unsafe things are by pratfalling on them and crying for attention. Convinced he's the victim of a conspiracy, Boom leaves a wake of parent worry in his path, forcing Boss to stop him.

programme.title: The Croods Family Tree Ep4
programme.desc: What Goes Eep Must Come Dawn - After a crowverine gliding mishap, Dawn loses her confidence and tells Eep she's taking a break from adventures. Eep convinces Dawn to join her on one last adventure climbing Grrr Mountain.

programme.title: The Croods Family Tree Ep5
programme.desc: Parental Stridence - When Hope oversteps by trying to teach Sandy manners, Ugga gets her revenge by challenging Hope to do the impossible: civilize Thunk.

programme.title: Abominable And The Invisible City Ep5

Ultimately, Jin foregoes his ceremony and instead delivers Mortys five babies.

programme.title: Dragons 9 Realms Ep2
programme.desc: First Flight: Part 2 - Tom forges a friendship with the dragon and discovers an entire world of dragons within the fissure.

Unfortunately, Krupp has run off to Ecuador to look for a fabled fountain. So the boys form the M.I.S.F.A.R.T.S. - Mega Incredible Search Force Adventure Rescue Team Squad - to travel to Ecuador and bring Krupp back, whether he wants it or not.

programme.title: Kung Fu Panda: The Dragon Knight Ep2
programme.desc: The Knights Code - Po and Blade's personalities clash as they track Klaus and Veruca and fight off some of Po's old foes. Blade gets to see Po's kung fu mastery, but doesn't agree to team up with him until she realizes that he accidentally holds the key to finding Klaus and Veruca: he has a piece of the WuGao Gauntlet. Meanwhile, Klaus and Veruca continue on their path of destruction while looking for the mysterious "Lotus".

programme.title: Kung Fu Panda: The Dragon Knight Ep3
programme.desc: The Lotus - Po's moral lines are blurred when he and Blade have to break an untrustworthy hedgehog monk (Zhen) out of jail to get more information on what Klaus and Veruca stole from the Lotus. They learn from Zhen that there are in fact three more weapons, and Po recognizes one of them from a comic book.

programme.title: Kung Fu Panda: The Dragon Knight Ep4
programme.desc: The Legend of Master Long-Tooth - Po and Blade must convince a deceased comic book writer's son to give them information about an unreleased comic that may point them toward the next weapon: a whip of fire. However, after the events of 103 Po is now a wanted criminal, so the Emperor's Forbidden Company arrives and captures him. Torn between saving Po and the mission she's sworn to complete, Blade flees and abandons Po.

Noddy uses all his investigating skills of who, what, where, when, why and how to work out that the wall must have been painted by someone very tall who likes the colour blue. Smartysaurus! She admits she painted it so that she could be better at hide-and-seek! Noddy helps her to understand that she can play the game without having to cheat. Thank you Noddy!

Waiting for the bulb is lighthouse keeper Chris Beacon and his pet parrot Micawber, both anxious to get the lighthouse working before sundown, and tracking a storm blowing in. Out at sea are Alf and PC Selby, enjoying a day's fishing, until they drift off-course and need the lighthouse to guide them ashore...

Tag helps train him (and his tail), and they even track down Master Wag who gives Scooch a good luck charm. But when Scooch loses the good luck charm before his tail-kwondo test, he needs to find a way to believe in himself.

programme.title: Dragons: Rescue Riders Ep23

Along the way, she becomes entangled in a passionate struggle with her former love, Gao Xiu Yu, while her return brings about new fates for those from her past.
